data.description: Welcome to this charming home in the beautiful city of Port Orange, FL! This lovely property features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious 1,664 square feet of living space. Step inside and be amazed by the open floor plan, allowing for seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The floor plan offers privacy with the master suite situated on one side of the home and the additional bedrooms on the other. Cozy up on chilly evenings by the brick wood burning fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The fenced back yard provides a safe space for family and pets to play, while also offering privacy for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. All three bedrooms boast walk-in closets, providing ample storage space for your belongings. The home has been updated with brand new luxury vinyl plank (LVP) and tile floors, adding a touch of modern elegance. Rest easy knowing that both the roof and HVAC system were replaced in 2023, ensuring years of worry-free living. Perfectly situated, this home is close to schools and shopping, making it ideal for families and those who value convenience. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home! Schedule a showing today and experience the joy of homeownership in this Port Orange gem.
